Subject: Easy tip to replacing fuel vent line.....

     Remove the four nuts holding the left rear tail light to easily
access the red vent line shown here:
http://homepage.mac.com/ratwell/.Pictures/FuelHose/09-FuelBreatherHoses.jpg

Couldn't find this in the Bentley.  Hopefully other's can benifit
instead of struggling like I did initially :)  Nice to smell fuel and
get a headache when taking a drive.  Tip applies to '78 and related models.


Troy
